      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 7th level, you constantly emanate a menacing aura while you're not &amp;Reference[condition=incapacitated]. The aura extends 10 feet from you in every direction, but not through &amp;Reference[rule=totalcover]{total cover}.</p><p>If a creature is &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] of you, its speed is reduced to 0 while in the aura, and that creature takes psychic damage equal to half your paladin level if it starts its turn there.</p><p>At 18th level, the range of this aura increases to 30 feet.</p></div>",
